== Installation ==

1. Upload the plugin folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory.
2. Activate the plugin through the Plugins menu in WordPress.
3. That's it ! you can now configure the plugin.

== Frequently Asked Questions ==

= Does your plugin set estimated delivery dates for a group of products? =

Yes. You can do that by using Shipping Classes Settings page.

= Can I select the operational days of the week for estimation? =

Yes. You can select the operational days using the 'Working Days' multi-select field provided in the general settings page.

